root: ^The player pulls down the panel to find a make-shift keypad of old wires and an archaic display. They are propmpted to enter a key. Not knowing what else to do...

freedom: ^With a whoosh and a large amount of steam, one of the walls slides down, freeing you into what appears to be a circular warehouse style building. It appears that there are a number of void-like holding cells on each level of this circular warehouse. There are almost imperceptably many levels to this warehouse.
